span style=\"font-size: medium;\">зҲҶзҷјж”»ж“Ҡ(и“„еҠӣ)еҸҜд»Ҙз ҙзӣҫпјҢд№ҹеҸҜд»ҘеӨ§е№…жёӣе°‘OD(жҠҖиғҪж§Ҫ)<br />\n<br />\nзҙ…иүІй җиӯҰеңҲеҸҜд»ҘдҪҝз”ЁжҠҖиғҪз„Ўж•өе№Җж“ӢдҪҸпјҢзҙ«иүІзҡ„дёҚиЎҢ<br />\nжҳҸиҝ·&mdash;&mdash;еҸ—еҲ°ж”»ж“ҠеҫҢж–№еҸҜи§ЈйҷӨ<br />\nй»‘жҡ—&mdash;&mdash;е‘ҪдёӯзҺҮдёӢйҷҚ<br />\nжҝ•иә«&mdash;&mdash;еҝ…иў«жҡҙж“Ҡ<br />\nеҶ°еҮҚ&mdash;&mdash;иў«еҗҢдјҙж”»ж“ҠеҫҢеҸҜи§ЈйҷӨ</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aYYRo2b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaYYRo2b.png&h=840bfb17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">йҰ–жҠҪжҺЁи–Ұ</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nиҺүиҺүгҖҒе…үеҘ¶гҖҒе…үж–§<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/07/105551_ba600461034f4a911e4caa6f5146fc76.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F07%2F105551_ba600461034f4a911e4caa6f5146fc76.png&h=10063ee9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nзҒ«еҲҖеҘі<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/07/105459_127dbc08891f2c5d801fa59ec6f87681.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F07%2F105459_127dbc08891f2c5d801fa59ec6f87681.gif&h=bd896583&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nж°ҙж§Қ<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nY01aws.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnY01aws.jpg&h=e912a611&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nйўЁеј“<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HCMj3rG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHCMj3rG.jpg&h=4567c144&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nжҡ—еј“<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h3SGayd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh3SGayd.jpg&h=d29b9437&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nUseful link<br />\nWiki: <a href=\"https://dragalialost.gamepedi